snippet.title: Swarm (PC) Gameplay
snippet.description:
OK... I think I've finally configured OBS on my new gaming laptop. And to celebrate, I might as well make another gameplay video. And what better way to do this than with one of the most obscure games I can remember.

I remember my Dad used to play this one back in the early/mid 2000's  - where it was packaged under the name "Galactic Swarm" - and I myself played it a couple of times. Of course, back then I wasn't used to playing games with a keyboard and mouse so I couldn't get very far. Because of it's obscurity -  possibly due to its generic title - it took me FOREVER to track down information about it online. But thankfully I managed to order another copy on eBay, and it just arrived two days ago. It runs rather flawlessly in VMWare, and I managed to obtain my best score yet while recording. I hope you enjoy!
